&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="updated-m365-call-flow-visualizer">Updated M365 Call Flow Visualizer
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>I&amp;rsquo;ve updated the M365 Call Flow Visualizer to support nested voice apps which don&amp;rsquo;t have associated resource accounts anymore.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://heusser.pro/p/m365-call-flow-visualizer-update-support-nested-voice-apps-without-resource-accounts-hjm1e1w9m0h8/Demo_AA_CallFlow-1.png"
width="6790"
height="6910"
